title: Drive-Thru Dolphin Spa
description:
Why is Mindy lassoing a drive thru car wash?! And what does this have to do with dolphins?! Find out the WOW of how coral mucus can help keep the skin of dolphins happy and healthy! It's the who, what, when, where, how, and WOW of coral mucus!
